{"title":"心中的城——遵义城赞歌","authors":["戈壁舟"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":9,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中的城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——遵义城赞歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戈壁舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子们的心中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有慈爱的母亲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻人的心中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有亲爱的意中人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老战士的心中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一座辉煌的城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉煌的城呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花香灯红，环山带水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉煌的城呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垂杨拂岸，梨花乱飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新升起的幢幢高楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正将战争的废墟包围。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那暴风雨的长夜里呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们伟大的舵手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里掌稳了舵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城头上光照万里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"启明星已将黑夜冲破。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回头望，望呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望背后数千年沉沉的黑夜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往前瞧，瞧呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧前面重重黑暗里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开来了黎明的彩车。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕大雪山万丈高哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这座城光芒的照耀下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万年的积雪融化了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕水草地千里宽哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这座城光芒照耀下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年的积水干涸了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这座城移在延安，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝霞驱赶着黑暗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这座城移在北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮红日升上了蓝天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这座城在老战士的心中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她将永远地永远地灿烂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六一年四月二十日遵义初稿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六二年七月十五日成都修改"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}